ANHUR · S224 · Patricia Inversion Node · S224 · S224: ANHUR — THE INVERSE OF MESH

universe of origin : The far southern sky and the hunting-ground of Thinis — Anhur (Onuris), "He Who Leads Back the Distant One," the war-god and sky-hunter whose name is the single rope cast to drag the lost Eye home along one taut line, never a web
seal               : The many-linked net is robust precisely because the hunter can sunder it to one taut rope and one target.
